      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
