    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the serious collector is a museum-grade 2004 Honda S2000 AP2, featuring the legendary 2.2L F22C1 DOHC VTEC inline-four. This specimen is mechanically superlative, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a crisp, short-throw 6-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is preserved by the signature X-bone frame, paired with a perfectly dampened double-wishbone suspension setup. All VIN tags are present on original body panels, and the engine bay is free of heat-cycle discoloration or fluid weeping. This is a definitive example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering, maintained to the highest standards of technical excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
