      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle is in breathtaking, showroom-fresh condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the leather is supple with no signs of creasing, and the original factory scent lingers. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a complete, documented service history with every milestone addressed by certified master technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. Complete with all original manuals, both keys, and a clean title. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a flawless, museum-quality example.",
